comments: Fox (SAC) initiates marginal contact to Mitchell's (CLE) body as he is dribbling on the perimeter.
Monk (SAC) reaches in and makes contact to Garland's (CLE) head/face area during his drive. The contact affects Garland's SQBR.
Huerter (SAC) establishes himself in Mitchell's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Garland (CLE) legally contests Huerter's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) initiates marginal body contact to Mitchell's (CLE) lower body at the start of his drive. Mitchell is able to move through the contact without his SQBR being affected.
Fox (SAC) moves alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and jumps vertically to contest his shot attempt in the lane.
During the rebound attempt, Mitchell (CLE) initiates contact with Sabonis' (SAC) upper body and dislodges him from his position.
Mitchell (CLE) initiates body contact with Sabonis (SAC) that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Fox (SAC) engages and disengages with Mitchell (CLE) and marginal contact occurs during the screen, as the pass is entered it is cleanly deflected by Fox (SAC).
Monk (SAC) brings his hands toward LeVert (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as Monk (SAC) moves towards the pick.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his hands toward LeVert (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis (SAC) releases away to roll.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Monk (SAC) throws an errant pass and it goes out of bounds.
LeVert (CLE) reaches in and initiates contact with Barnes' (SAC) arm as he attempts to get to the inbound pass.
Mitchell (CLE) brings his off-arm toward Huerter (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Mitchell releases away without applying any force.
